.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, banana, artichoke, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, singing, skydiving, writing
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, horse, rabbit
1. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the person eating banana##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
7. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | artichoke   | grapes      | banana       | strawberry |
| Hobby   | video-games | writing | skydiving     | singing |
| Pet     | rabbit     | goat  | ferret | horse |

