.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, fanta, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, scientific, horror
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, pony, dog
1. the owner of the pony is the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking water##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta   | milk          | water | almond-milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | adventure | horror   | documentary     |
| Pet           | mouse | lizard         | dog         | pony |

