.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, board-games, fishing, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, dressmaker, project-manager, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, reggae, funk, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
2. the project-manager is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the entrepreneur is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the lawyer and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games | photography      | fishing       | traveling    |
| Job           | dressmaker  | project-manager  | entrepreneur | lawyer |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | funk | reggae         | pop    |

