.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, juice, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, security-guard, lawyer, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tea-polo, cricket, lacrosse
1. the designer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the designer##3
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the person who's sport is tea-polo is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the designer##1
7. the designer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
8. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
9. the fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate         | milk  | juice     | tea         |
| Job        | fisherman | security-guard | designer | lawyer         |
| Sport      | tea-polo         | cricket  | soccer   | lacrosse |

