.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, dubstep, house
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, thai, spanish, brazilian
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, chinchilla, bird
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 2. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 4. the spanish is between the fan of disco and the fan of jazz##2
 5. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the owner of the bird is the fan of dubstep##1
 7. the brazilian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 9. the thai is between the fan of house and the fan of dubstep##2
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | dubstep    | disco | house    |
| Nationality   | dutch | spanish | thai  | brazilian |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | bird    | turtle        | hamster   |

