.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, iced-tea, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, police-officer, electrician, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indian, malaysian, egyptian
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
2. the police-officer is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the electrician##3
4. the police-officer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the analyst##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the indian is on the left of the police-officer##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the indian##3
9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite                | cola  | mirinda | iced-tea   |
| Job           | lawyer | police-officer | analyst   | electrician |
| Nationality   | indian         | canadian     | egyptian     | malaysian |

