.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cauliflower, carrot, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, documentary, family, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, gospel, hip-hop, blues
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the fan of metal is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of blues##2
6. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating plum is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | carrot    | cauliflower  | mango  | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | documentary | zombie | family |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | metal     | blues    | gospel |

