.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, colombian, canadian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, ferret, snake
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking mirinda and the russian##2
2. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
3. the canadian is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
7. the russian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
8. the canadian is the person drinking water##1
9. the mexican is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | water | mirinda      | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | colombian | mexican | russian |
| Pet           | snake      | ferret       | guinea-pig   | mouse      |

