.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, reading, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, brazilian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, soccer, parkour, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the thai is between the person who's sport is baseball and the colombian##2
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | reading | fishing  | photography  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | spanish       | thai | colombian |
| Sport         | parkour   | baseball      | tennis | soccer       |

