3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person drinking coffee is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
6. the person watching western movies is the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
