.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, water, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rugby, ice-hockey, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, subway, trike
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | water    | hot-chocolate     | 7up    | juice        |
| Sport       | ice-hockey   | parkour | rugby | skiing |
| Transport   | trike | subway      | jet-ski    | taxi   |

