.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, grapes, papaya, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, photography, chess
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog, ferret
1. the person eating mango is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the person eating grapes is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating mango##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | papaya    | grapes    | mango  | asparagus |
| Hobby   | chess | woodworking | fishing | photography      |
| Pet     | fish   | chinchilla        | ferret   | hedgehog       |

 